verbose_text: To evaluate the time dependent effects of high glucose, the MCs were cultured with 100 muM glucose and harvested at 0, 12, 24 and 36 h. To evaluate the dose dependent effects of high glucose, the MCs were cultured with various concentrations of glucose (0, 50, 100 and 200 muM) and harvested at 24 h. Subsequently, RT-qPCR and western blot analysis were performed to measure the expression levels of SOX6 and miR-342-3p.
